name: AMP-UP™ ACRYLIC
description:
AMP-UP™ ACRYLIC Low VOC High Gloss Enamel is a single component, environmentally friendly, and water-based styrenated acrylic enamel designed
for interior and exterior industrial and commercial use on adequately primed surfaces. AMP-UP™ ACRYLIC, when used in conjunction with AMP-UPTM products, protects steel, aluminum and concrete in mild to moderate industrial environments. This coating exhibits excellent
adhesion, gloss retention, flexibility, and corrosion and UV resistance
